Uses of Package
com.hazelcast.durableexecutor

  • Packages that use com.hazelcast.durableexecutor 
    Package Description
    com.hazelcast.core
    Provides core API interfaces/classes.
    com.hazelcast.durableexecutor
    This package contains DurableExecutorService functionality for Hazelcast.
    The DurableExecutorService extends the ExecutorService and provides additional methods like executing tasks on a member who is owner of a specific key.
    com.hazelcast.instance
    This package contains Hazelcast Instance functionality.
  • Classes in com.hazelcast.durableexecutor used by com.hazelcast.core 
    Class and Description
    DurableExecutorService
    Durable implementation of ExecutorService.
  • Classes in com.hazelcast.durableexecutor used by com.hazelcast.durableexecutor 
    Class and Description
    DurableExecutorServiceFuture
    A Future where one can obtain the task ID for tracking the response.
  • Classes in com.hazelcast.durableexecutor used by com.hazelcast.instance
